    <briefdescription>
<para>Sequential binary reader for deserializing message fields. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Reads values contiguously from a byte buffer. Strings are read as length-prefixed (uint32_t). Trivially copyable types are read via memcpy.</para>
